Creating Word Cloud

Data Cleaning

The data is cleaned in order to use it for the word cloud.

result.text <- sapply(result.term, function(x) x$getText())
result.text <- gsub("rt", "", result.text)
result.text <- gsub("@\\w+", "", result.text)
result.text <- gsub("[[:punct:]]", "", result.text)
result.text <- gsub("http\\w+", "", result.text)
result.text <- gsub("[ |\t]{2,}", "", result.text)
result.text <- gsub("^ ", "", result.text)
result.text <- gsub(" $", "", result.text)
result.text <- tolower(result.text)

Stop words removal

result.text.corpus <- Corpus(VectorSource(result.text))
result.text.corpus <- tm_map(result.text.corpus, function(x) removeWords(x,stopwords()))

Word Cloud Generation

wordcloud(result.text.corpus, min.freq = 2, scale=c(7,0.5),colors=brewer.pal(8, "Dark2"),  random.color= TRUE, random.order = FALSE, max.words = 150)

Sentiment Analysis

Reading Positive and Negative Words

neg <- scan("negative-words.txt", what = "character", comment.char = ";")
pos <- scan("positive-words.txt", what = "character", comment.char = ";")

Scoring Tweets Function

score.sentiment <- function(result.text, pos.words, neg.words)

{
scores = laply(result.text, function(result.text, pos.words, neg.words) {

result.text <- gsub('https://','',result.text)
result.text <- gsub('[^[:graph:]]', ' ',result.text)
result.text <- gsub('[[:cntrl:]]', '', result.text)
result.text <- gsub('\\d+', '', result.text)
result.text <- str_replace_all(result.text,"[^[:graph:]]", " ") 

word.list <- str_split(result.text, '\\s+')
words <- unlist(word.list)
pos.matches <- match(words, pos.words) 
neg.matches <- match(words, neg.words)
pos.matches <- !is.na(pos.matches)
neg.matches <- !is.na(neg.matches)
 
score <- sum(pos.matches) - sum(neg.matches)
 
return(score)
 
}, pos.words, neg.words )
 
scores.df = data.frame(score=scores, text=result.text)
 
return(scores.df)
 
}
analysis <- score.sentiment(result.text, pos, neg)

Plotting Sentiment Scores

table(analysis$score)
## 
##  -5  -4  -3  -2  -1   0   1   2   3   4 
##   1   4   4  22 137 988 613 163  58  10
hist(analysis$score)
